&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Position Summary&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The DevOps Engineer is responsible for ensuring the availability, scalability, security, and operational reliability of iRely&#39;s software platforms and supporting infrastructure.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role will design and manage cloud infrastructure, deployment pipelines, monitoring, disaster recovery, and automation practices that support highly available enterprise software solutions. Working closely with Development, QA, Product, and Architecture teams, this individual will help build and maintain modern cloud-based platforms utilizing React, TypeScript, C#, PostgreSQL, Azure, and multi-tenant SaaS architectures.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Success in this role will be measured by system reliability, deployment quality, recovery readiness, operational efficiency, and overall platform stability.&lt;/p&gt;
