&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design, maintain, and optimize highly available cloud infrastructure that supports business-critical software applications.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Implement monitoring, disaster recovery, backup, failover, and operational readiness processes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure platform performance, scalability, security, and reliability.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;CI/CD &amp;amp; Automation&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
