&lt;li&gt;Develop automation that improves deployment consistency, operational efficiency, and platform reliability.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support deployment strategies that minimize downtime and reduce operational risk.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
